## Limitations

This report is based on available data up to October 2023 and may not include the latest research findings. Additionally, while the sources used are credible, the report does not cover every aspect of vaccine safety research, focusing instead on key findings and general trends. Further research is recommended for a more comprehensive understanding of specific vaccines and their safety profiles.

